    "Name": "Beowulf IIC",
    "Details": "This design was the result of experimenting with integrating improved C3 computers into Clan designs. The base chassis, armor, and ground performance remain the same as the parent design, but the ER large pulse laser and light TAG were replaced with a standard ER large laser and C3i computer. This design was used by troops from the First Drak√∏ns on Labrea in 3099. The C3i technology was eventually removed from the factory by The Republic of the Sphere inspectors after exerting political pressure to stop using the equipment.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Extended Torso Twist</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.09</color></b>",
